    <meta name="description" content="Privacy Policy - ezSkins">
    <meta name="keywords" content="Privacy Policy, ezSkins">
    <title>ezSkins - Privacy Policy</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="../dist/img/favicon.png" type="image/x-icon">
    <!-- @import "../link.kit" -->
</head>

<body>
    <!-- @import "../nav-cases.kit" -->
    <main class="main">
        <!-- @import "../lastdrops.kit" -->
        <section class="wrapper" style="padding: 140px 0 60px;">
            <div class="main__container" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <h2 class="section__title section__title--cases"><span class="section__title-bg">Privacy Policy</span></h2>
                <div style="padding: 2em; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1); background: rgba(0,0,0,.15);">
                    <div style="line-height: 1.8; opacity: .9; color: rgba(255,255,255,.85);">
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5em; font-size: 1.1em;">
                            <strong>Last Updated: January 2026</strong>
                        </p>
                        
                        <h3 style="color: #fff; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 1.3em;">1. Introduction</h3>
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 1em;">
                            At ezSkins, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our platform.
                        </p>

                        <h3 style="color: #fff; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 1.3em;">2. Information We Collect</h3>
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 1em;">We collect the following types of information:</p>
                        
                        <h4 style="color: rgba(255,255,255,.9); margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; font-size: 1.1em;">2.1 Account Information</h4>
                        <ul style="margin-left: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; list-style-type: disc;">
                            <li>Nickname: Display name you choose when creating your account</li>
                            <li>Avatar: Profile picture URL or image you upload</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h4 style="color: rgba(255,255,255,.9); margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; font-size: 1.1em;">2.2 Game Data</h4>
                        <ul style="margin-left: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; list-style-type: disc;">
                            <li>Virtual balance and currency</li>
                            <li>Virtual items in your inventory</li>
                            <li>Game statistics (cases opened, battles created, upgrades, jackpots won)</li>
                            <li>Game history and transaction records</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h4 style="color: rgba(255,255,255,.9); margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; font-size: 1.1em;">2.3 Payment Information</h4>
                        <ul style="margin-left: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; list-style-type: disc;">
                            <li>Email address (when making deposits)</li>
                            <li>Deposit amounts and transaction history</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h4 style="color: rgba(255,255,255,.9); margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; font-size: 1.1em;">2.4 Technical Information</h4>
                        <ul style="margin-left: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; list-style-type: disc;">
                            <li>Browser type and version</li>
                            <li>Device information</li>
                            <li>IP address</li>
                            <li>Cookies and local storage data</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h3 style="color: #fff; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 1.3em;">3. How We Use Your Information</h3>
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 1em;">We use the collected information for the following purposes:</p>
                        <ul style="margin-left: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; list-style-type: disc;">
                            <li>To provide and maintain our gaming services</li>
                            <li>To process deposits and manage your account</li>
                            <li>To display your profile, statistics, and inventory</li>
                            <li>To improve and optimize our platform</li>
                            <li>To prevent fraud and ensure fair play</li>
                            <li>To communicate with you regarding your account or our services</li>
                            <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h3 style="color: #fff; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 1.3em;">4. Data Storage</h3>
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 1em;">
                            Your account data, including nickname, avatar, balance, items, and game statistics, is stored locally in your browser's local storage. This means your data is stored on your device and is not transmitted to external servers unless you explicitly make a deposit.
                        </p>

                        <h3 style="color: #fff; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 1.3em;">5. Cookies and Local Storage</h3>
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 1em;">
                            We use browser local storage to save your account information and game data. This allows you to access your account across browser sessions. You can clear your browser's local storage at any time, which will reset your account data.
                        </p>

                        <h3 style="color: #fff; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 1.3em;">6. Third-Party Services</h3>
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 1em;">
                            We may use third-party services such as Firebase for data storage and payment processors for deposit transactions. These services have their own privacy policies governing the use of your information.
                        </p>

                        <h3 style="color: #fff; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 1.3em;">7. Data Security</h3>
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 1em;">
                            We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure. While we strive to protect your data, we cannot guarantee absolute security.
                        </p>

                        <h3 style="color: #fff; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 1.3em;">8. Your Rights</h3>
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 1em;">You have the right to:</p>
                        <ul style="margin-left: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; list-style-type: disc;">
                            <li>Access your account data stored in local storage</li>
                            <li>Update your nickname and avatar at any time</li>
                            <li>Clear your local storage, which will reset your account</li>
                            <li>Delete your account by clearing your browser's local storage</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h3 style="color: #fff; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 1.3em;">9. Children's Privacy</h3>
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 1em;">
                            ezSkins is not intended for users under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us.
                        </p>

                        <h3 style="color: #fff; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 1.3em;">10. Data Retention</h3>
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 1em;">
                            Your account data is stored locally in your browser until you clear your local storage or delete your browser data. We do not retain your data on our servers unless you make a deposit, in which case payment information may be retained as required by law.
                        </p>

                        <h3 style="color: #fff; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 1.3em;">11. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h3>
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 1em;">
                            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date.
                        </p>

                        <h3 style="color: #fff; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 1.3em;">12. Contact Us</h3>
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 1em;">
                            If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us through our official channels.
                        </p>

                        <p style="margin-top: 2em; padding-top: 1.5em; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1); font-size: 0.9em; opacity: .7;">
                            By using ezSkins, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
